data.description: Welcome to your new haven in the heart of Spring Valley! This lovely 4-bedroom home exudes curb appeal & offers the perfect blend of modern comforts & classic elegance. Step inside to gleaming hardwood floors & a beautifully designed kitchen with sleek granite counters. The main bedroom features a convenient private door to the outside & an abundance of closets. Low-maintenance landscaping minimizes your upkeep. Close to Lamar County Park & major freeways! Supplement: The curb appeal of this home is exceptional, with a welcoming porch that beckons you inside. Enjoy ample parking & yard space, making this home perfect for entertaining or relaxing in your own private paradise. The kitchen is a chef’s delight with a great flow, crisp white cabinets, & beautiful granite counters. Well-maintained by the current owners, all 4 bedrooms are spacious including the main suite which boasts an ensuite bathroom with walk-in shower. The fenced backyard features beautiful hardscaping that wraps around the outside of the home. Low-maintenance turf ensures you spend more time enjoying your property than doing yard work! Convenient to downtown & most places in San Diego County!
